{
  "texts": [
    "Generally speaking, one can classify misinformation datasets into 3 annotation schemes.",
    "Listed from most fine-grained to most coarse-grained:",
    "Claim: experts fact-check individual (but complete) statements in isolation.",
    "Claims are usually small spans sourced from larger documents or utterances 2.",
    "Article: experts label the overall veracity of entire documents."
  ]
}